          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Audit énergétique</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Audit réglementaire et volontaire NF EN 16247 : identification des gisements, plan d'actions CEE et conformité décret tertiaire.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Free cooling -->
        <a href="/expertises/free-cooling/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Free cooling</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Refroidissement naturel par l'air extérieur pour data centers et process industriels. Économies 30–60 % sur le compresseur, prime CEE IND-UT-117.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Froid industriel -->
        <a href="/expertises/froid-industriel/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Froid industriel</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Modernisation des installations frigorifiques industrielles : groupes à vis, chambres froides, surgélation. Primes CEE IND-UT-136 et ROI 3 à 7 ans.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Mobilité électrique -->
        <a href="/expertises/mobilite-electrique/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Mobilité électrique</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Bornes de recharge IRVE pour flottes et parkings d'entreprise. Financement via primes CEE IND-UT-131 et BAT-EQ-131, ROI 3 à 6 ans.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Régulation chauffage -->
        <a href="/expertises/regulation-chauffage/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 13.5V3.75m0 9.75a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3m0-3a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3m0 3.75V16.5m12-3V3.75m0 9.75a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3m0-3a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3m0 3.75V16.5m-6-9V3.75m0 3.75a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3m0-3a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3m0 9.75V10.5" /></svg>
